Application: Cascade Multi-Hop
  Description: A to B to C all cascade. Static check passes (no restrict involved).
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000004

Identity:
  Scopes are "mh.view", "mh.manage", "mh.delete"
  A "tester" has "mh.view", "mh.manage", and "mh.delete"

Content called "as":
  Each a has a label which is text, required
  Anyone with "mh.view" can view as
  Anyone with "mh.manage" can create as
  Anyone with "mh.delete" can delete as

Content called "bs":
  Each b has a label which is text, required
  Each b has an a which references as, required, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "mh.view" can view bs
  Anyone with "mh.manage" can create bs

Content called "cs":
  Each c has a label which is text, required
  Each c has a b which references bs, required, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "mh.view" can view cs
  Anyone with "mh.manage" can create cs
